OL,3,CHuman error 'in general' caused fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, defendant says
OL,6,FThe collision between the Condor
OL,7,FCommodore Goodwill Ferry and L'Ecume
OL,8,FII could have been avoided if the
OL,9,Fdefendants had acted differently,
OL,10,FJersey's Royal Court has heard.
OL,12,FLewis Peter Carr has been giving
OL,13,Fevidence on the second day of the
OL,14,Fdefence trial, where he and another
OL,15,Fman, Artur Sevash-Zade, are accused of
OL,16,Fthe manslaughter of three Jersey
OL,17,Ffishermen back in December 2022. They
OL,18,Fboth deny all the charges.
