OL,3,CHuman error 'in general' caused fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, defendant says
OL,6,FAt the Royal Court on Tuesday 16
OL,7,FSeptember, Mr Carr continued to give
OL,8,Fhis account of the events after he
OL,9,Fdecided to take the stand.
OL,11,FHe told the jury that at the time of
OL,12,Fthe incident, he had felt rested and
OL,13,Falert enough to take watch.
OL,15,FAdvocate Simon Thomas, defending Mr
OL,16,FCarr, asked him why he believed the
OL,17,Fcollision occurred.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
