OL,3,CHuman error 'in general' caused fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, defendant says
OL,6,FMr Carr responded that he believed it
OL,7,Fwas due to L'Ecume II not displaying
OL,8,Fits fishing lights and that there was
OL,9,Fno effective lookout on the trawler,
OL,10,Fin terms of someone who understood the
OL,11,FInternational Regulations for
OL,12,FPreventing Collisions at Sea.
OL,14,FThe defendant also told the court that
OL,15,Factions taken by the smaller fishing
OL,16,Fvessel, when she altered course in a
OL,17,Fport direction in the final minutes
OL,18,Fbefore the collision, were not
OL,19,Fcompliant with those same regulations.
