OL,3,CHuman error 'in general' caused fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, defendant says
OL,6,FMr Carr was also questioned by
OL,7,FAdvocate Mike Preston, who is
OL,8,Frepresenting the other defendant, Mr
OL,9,FSevash-Zade.
OL,11,FThe court has previously heard that
OL,12,Fboth defendants were on lookout on the
OL,13,Fbridge the morning of the incident,
OL,14,Fbut Mr Carr had sent Mr Sevash-Zade
OL,15,Faway for breakfast before the
OL,16,Fcollision.
