OL,3,CHuman error 'in general' caused fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, defendant says
OL,6,FAdvocate Preston asked if Mr Carr was
OL,7,Fin charge of the management team, to
OL,8,Fwhich he agreed, and confirmed that he
OL,9,Fwas also responsible for keeping a
OL,10,Flookout.
OL,12,FMr Carr also agreed with Advocate
OL,13,FPreston that he was responsible for
OL,14,Fmaintaining an all-around watch whilst
OL,15,Fon the bridge.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
