OL,3,CHuman error 'in general' caused fatal
OL,4,Cboat collision, defendant says
OL,6,FThe court heard Mr Carr confirm that
OL,7,Fthere was nothing with the weather and
OL,8,Fsea conditions or the state of the
OL,9,Fvessel which would have hindered the
OL,10,Fability to manoeuvre the Condor
OL,11,FCommodore Goodwill Ferry.
OL,13,FMr Carr also confirmed that he had
OL,14,Ftaken an eight-hour break before his
OL,15,Fshift, and he thought he was fit and
OL,16,Falert to do the job, but said he was
OL,17,F"not sure" whether his actions were
OL,18,Faffected by fatigue.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
