OL,4,Cboat collision, defendant says
OL,6,FMr Carr replied: "With hindsight, yes,
OL,7,Fit could have been avoided," but added
OL,8,Flater that he had "closely" monitored
OL,9,Fthe situation.
OL,11,FBoth Lewis Peter Carr and Artur Sevash-
OL,12,FZade plead not guilty to all charges,
OL,13,Fand the trial continues.
